Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:27.53,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}Dear Yui-senpai, I've finally made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.14,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}1, 2, 3, 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.80,Overlap,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1\pos(354,346)}I'll do my best, Senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:36.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Though there are too many people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.33,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}What's wrong Tomo? You aren't scared, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, it's not like you, Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:46.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Shut up. Unlike Saya, this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.73,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}You have to enjoy yourself at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.67,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}So, so. Let's enjoy! Right, Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.73,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh Yumi, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Come on, hold yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.00,Overlap,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(348,347)}What should i do? What should i do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yumi, it'll be fine. Now relax...just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.25,Overlap,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,347)}Áh, I wonder if this means there'll be fewer rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:18.51,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(345,378)\i1}Senpai, I may be you junior right now, but i'm not backing down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.87,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}Because i swore i'd be able to sing the songs you wrote.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:29.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tomo! Wake up already! You're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:34.88,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ouch. What? Uh-oh! Mom, couldn't you have waken me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:49.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}Dear Yui-senpai, my high school life has just started, so i'm not used to it yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh? I have to brush my teeth again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.05,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}My studies have also become much harder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.05,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah! Oh no, Isn't there a test today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:22.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}But i've already made friends. Making friends is one of my skills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.37,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:25.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Morning Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.03,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Seriously, what are we going to do about today's test?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hmmm? I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:33.27,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Eh? And do you think that's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.69,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I guess. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.49,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ta dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.06,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hu-huh? Isn't that Himuro Shinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I scored some tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:50.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:53.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yay! Thank you Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:55.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh? Why do you think i'm taking you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh? So you're going alone then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:58.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.30,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course, i'm going with my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:06.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh. Then you shouldn't be showing off your tickets like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh yeah, have you decided on what clubs to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.32,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Nope. Our school's clubs are just lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}How about music, since you're good at singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}If there were a karaoke club... Miki-chan, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Me? I thought i'd go take a look at the archery club today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Archery?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}She's there. Torowa-sama that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.29,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}How can Suwa-senpai be so incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:39.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Even though the Lemon Angels broke up, she should've continued to sing solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:40.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:46.52,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}They say that she's the only daughter of a diplomat, and has lived in many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:49.91,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Which is why she's fluent in German and English.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:54.12,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Her hobbies are tea ceremonies, horse back riding, flower arranging, ballroom dancing and piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.66,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Like a true celebrity princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:07:00.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}She's won a lot of awards at piano competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.87,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh? That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.54,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Shhh! She's about to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}W-W-Woah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:12.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.96,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tomo, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}What? Did you do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.22,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}What do you mean by "again"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.64,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}But you were scolded yesterday too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.30,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yesterday was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:36.73,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was doing ballet and used a little too much strength, and the classroom window just popped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.19,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:45.12,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Today i just slipped on some stairs and there was a painter there re-painting the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just picturing that is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.79,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wow, you high school students are a cut above.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:56.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh? Oh this? You're wrong, this is just a hobby of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:02.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yup. Oh, hey, i finished a new song. Want to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:03.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's just a short little melody of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wow, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}The song's called "Evolution."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,375)}This has a nice rhythm to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:53.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(350,371)}Actually, though it's not official, this'll be a debut song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.73,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh? When did this get decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:59.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah, sorry, sorry. Not me. The one to debut is her -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:04.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Suwa Miki. We became friends in an online programmer community.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.24,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}This is a co-operative effort between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.29,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Right now she's living overseas, but will be returning next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.29,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}When she gets here, i'll have to introduce you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.33,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}though she may be a little hard to get along with initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:22.26,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}She'll be back and will attend Hakuo H.S. next year, so why don't all three of us go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:26.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Amh uh,i don't think i could...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:31.14,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}What are you saying? You shouldn't give up without trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tomo, you should be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah, uh, umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:43.61,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.35,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Uh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}"Wait for me", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sound off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:57.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Fight! Oh! Fight! Oh! Fight! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.35,Overlap,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(353,351)}Hey, you freshman, you're not keeping up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:58.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(356,383)}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Fight! Oh! Fight! Oh! Fight! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.92,Overlap,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(351,351)}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(349,382)}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:05.13,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(351,378)}Fight! Oh! Fight! Oh! Fight! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:05.34,Overlap,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1\pos(354,348)}Dear Yui-senpai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.70,Overlap,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1\pos(352,349)}I thought i had gotten over it already,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:15.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}but i guess i'm hopeless, my memories keep coming back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:17.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I thought you'd be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}You must really like it up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:22.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Do you want to walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.61,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}If so, then i have to turn this in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:29.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh? A new club membership notice? That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wait for me at the gates, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:32.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Suwa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:32.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Kya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.01,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:50.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Eh, ah, Su,Su-Su, hello. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I...I'm Minaguchi Tomo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.24,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Uh, well i was on the roof and i heard the song you were playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:00.54,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Uh, not that being on the roof was worth mentioning. Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:04.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,384)}Um, i just wanted to say that the song you were playing was "Evolution".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.88,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I liked the song since way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:11.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Uh, not just the song, but i like all of Yui-senpai's songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:16.35,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm not sure how to put this, but i get a nice, good feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:21.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(349,382)}Ah, and why is it i'm talking about Yui-senpai? Well, i'll start explaining all of that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:29.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,383)}That is, i'm Yui-senpai's junior. Ah, i guess that's obvious since she's my Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:36.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Umm, and i've heard all about you from her, so i thought i'd like to meet you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:42.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(347,384)}I was so worried about what sort of person you would be, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:48.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(357,385)}Umm, back at the archery field, you were really cool. Really impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:51.26,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Um, that is to say i have the utmost respect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:54.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're good at studying, singing, playing the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.26,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Umm, uh err...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:02.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Uh, what am i going on about...i don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're awfully noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:10.69,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I hate people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:20.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Please, never speak to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:32.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}Dear Yui-senpai, could it be i've gotten on her bad side?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:40.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah, it's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.14,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}There's no way i can fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:48.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,384)}Cheer up. I'll become friends with Suwa-senpai, and make an appeal on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'll tell her Tomo isn't all that bad of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Mmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:56.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Besides, it was probably because she was in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:14:00.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}But she didn't have to say she hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:03.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}We have only just met. It wasn't very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:08.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}"Please never speak to me again."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.46,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Now, there, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:13.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:18.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}How could the old leader of the Lemon Angels act like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:22.93,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(350,382)}Maybe the reason the Lemon Angels broke up was because of her bad personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Eh? Ah, yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:30.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah, now i'm pissed! What id i do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:36.03,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I may have been a little noisy, but it didn't warrant that speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:43.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, calm down a lttle. I'll treat you to some Shiffon Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Really, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}You got over that quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.72,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:01.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yuki-chan, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.02,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}We're being followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:07.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:08.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's probably a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.82,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:40.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.26,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Save me. There's a strange man stalking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.22,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Kyaa, pervert! Why you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Kogure-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.83,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah, isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm fine. He really is a record maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:13.91,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}It looks like this'll take some time, Yuki-chan,so go on home without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:17.30,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, yeah. Well, i'll see you tomorrow. Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ouch... Minaguchi-san, you're pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:27.41,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Now, now. Let's start over. I'm Kogure Ryota. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Woah, you're an important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:33.41,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}You surely don't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:34.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sorry to disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}By the way, you know about the Lemon Angels, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}So, do you know the reason for their sudden break-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:46.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:55.29,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Actually right now there's a project to create a new Lemon Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, the Second Lemon Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,383)}We'll be keeping the same leader as before, but the rest will be completely new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:08.75,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}By leader, you mean Suwa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:13.41,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(346,386)}That's right. And for the new members, we're planning on holding an audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}So, would you like to give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:17.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.87,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Would you mind giving the Lemon Angel auditions a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:29.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,388)}Now hold on a moment. My chances of becoming a Lemon Angel are hopeless. Absolutely hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:38.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}To be honest, i thought so too, that you wouldn't easily succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}So why is it you asked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:47.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yui-senpai? You knew Yui-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:52.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(354,383)}Yeah, it was back when i was still an assistant, and i got involved in the creation of the first Lemon Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.52,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}That was when i got to talk with Yui about all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:18:01.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}She really wanted you to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.37,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}To sing the songs she made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:10.12,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(353,383)}What's with the uncertainty? You're now the only one that can make Yui and my dreams a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.29,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh? Dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.83,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's right! Dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:19.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,384)}It's what both Yui and i always thought about. The desire to make real music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just by listening to it, it would lend people strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:29.13,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I want to make such stupendous songs with the new Lemon Angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:33.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Right now there's no such thing as real music in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:39.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(352,382)}Current music is just trendy. One second they're popular, the next they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:43.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(356,383)}Aren't they just like mass produced "shake and bake" songs for the masses?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}I want to create something far different!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(346,386)}Something that will last decades, centuries as a great song! That's what i want to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:53.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Lemon Angels will become, as the name implies, Angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:57.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah! Angels will deliver music to the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.88,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(351,385)}Don't you think it would be great to be selected as a member of this elite band?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:07.91,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}There will certainly be difficult times, trials and hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:12.79,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}But if you overcome them, you'll be able to see the light ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,Text,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's where the music we create exists!
